<div id="review_1619589483" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1619589483" />
    <a title="Tink Magoo is bad at reviews" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews"><img alt="Tink Magoo is bad at reviews" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1597958182p2/38603325.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1619589483?book_show_action=true">Apr 08, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Tink Magoo is bad at reviews" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Tink Magoo is bad at reviews" href="/user/show/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews">Tink Magoo is bad at reviews</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/11554722-fever-1793">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=almost-got-my-tears">almost-got-my-tears</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=zzz-cover-grey">zzz-cover-grey</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=family-matters">family-matters</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=favourite-standalones">favourite-standalones</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=turned-my-brain-on">turned-my-brain-on</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=young-adult">young-adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=sex-none">sex-none</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38603325-tink-magoo-is-bad-at-reviews?shelf=job-waitress">job-waitress</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1619589483" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10960290187236667872"><br/>First a small ramble.<br/><br/>When I was at school I always thought <i>&apos;What do I want to learn history for, it&apos;s boring, where will it get me and what help will it be&apos;.</i> Just imagine if everyone had the same outlook, we would lose so much knowledge. Thankfully now I&apos;m an old withered up Mother I can appreciate our past a lot better. <br/><br/><b>&quot;Life was a battle, and Mother a tired and bitter captain&quot;</b><br/><br/>This story really punched me in the heart with its sorrow. And what really makes it hit home, is the fact that in this </span>
  <span id="freeText10960290187236667872" style="display:none"><br />First a small ramble.<br /><br />When I was at school I always thought <i>'What do I want to learn history for, it's boring, where will it get me and what help will it be'.</i> Just imagine if everyone had the same outlook, we would lose so much knowledge. Thankfully now I'm an old withered up Mother I can appreciate our past a lot better. <br /><br /><b>"Life was a battle, and Mother a tired and bitter captain"</b><br /><br />This story really punched me in the heart with its sorrow. And what really makes it hit home, is the fact that in this day and age people still suffer as badly as they did back in 1793. This evolved from the story of a hard done by teenager who resented her Mother for working her so hard, to a strong young lady finding hope where there seemed to be none.<br /><br />I can't express just how much I loved this.<br /><br /><b>"One had to be careful with elbows and boys"</b></span>
  <a data-text-id="10960290187236667872" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


