          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/10003.Laurie_Halse_Anderson"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1563830499p3/10003.jpg);'></div>
